OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain developing widely this
OL,6,Fmorning, turning heavy at times,
OL,7,Fthough the south and east becoming
OL,8,Fdrier for a time in the afternoon,
OL,9,Fbefore heavy rain returns later.
OL,10,FStrengthening winds with chance of
OL,11,Fgales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain soon clearing to
OL,14,Fscattered showers this evening. Chance
OL,15,Fof severe gales for a while then winds
OL,16,Feasing tonight, with most places
OL,17,Fbecoming dry.
OL,18,
OL,19,CSunday:FA brighter day with a mixture
OL,20,Fof sunny intervals and occasional
OL,21,Fshowers. Freshening westerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
